  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2604920/extras/7b5551689059d1962f0fe84e5eca0cb0.webp?t=1758801877\" width=350 height=58 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to your new job, NPC: Giving out quests to local adventurers!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose quests which are appropriate to their level to help them become mighty, and perhaps some day one of your clients will become the hero of the town.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2604920/extras/497de36451f9e9b604c542f995baa1fa.apng?t=1758801877\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2604920/extras/497de36451f9e9b604c542f995baa1fa.poster.avif?t=1758801877\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=331 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2604920/extras/922d6f1b49fbc472f6d1a0400bae485a.webp?t=1758801877\" width=350 height=58 /></span><br><strong>Each With Multiple Endings:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Get Fired</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Get Assassinated</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Destroy the Entire World</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Join a Cult</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Start a Mutiny</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ... and More!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>(A full playthrough is <strong>3-5 hours</strong>, a completionist run is 10+)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2604920/extras/c9117246b3fb9ff54473cabe40cd82f1.avif?t=1758801877\" width=600 height=331 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2604920/extras/dd3db32482d465606d7503aa2cbea3b0.webp?t=1758801877\" width=350 height=58 /></span><br><strong>Featuring Responsive Dialogue:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2604920/extras/8172e6a716d286b46118b7eede72eca0.poster.avif?t=1758801877\" width=600 height=331 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2604920/extras/8172e6a716d286b46118b7eede72eca0.webm?t=1758801877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2604920/extras/fbb5e37f1fc5dbc959d0d4fbe842c8ff.webp?t=1758801877\" width=350 height=58 /></span><br><strong>Who each have their own:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Personality</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Class & level</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Likes & dislikes</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2604920/extras/e71c714d51cb0c42306fea3f069479fe.poster.avif?t=1758801877\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2604920/extras/e71c714d51cb0c42306fea3f069479fe.webm?t=1758801877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><i>A selection of the world's mighty heroes! (aka not you.)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Accessibility:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playable with controller, mouse, keyboard, or hybrid</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playable with 1 or 2 hands</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Curvy font option for readability vs the traditional pixel font</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Option to adjust the text speed to show dialog fast vs. instantly</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2604920/extras/c41fd1d3a6573d801d82679816150301.webp?t=1758801877\" width=600 height=58 /></span></p>",
